Enkiroroto nairorie Solomon olorere

(
1   Ilai 
8  .
12  -
21  )


1  Neitoki Solomon ajo, “Etejo Olaitoriani kebik ninye te misimisi nagut. 
2  Aateshetaka nanu iyie enkaji e shumata, ewueji ino nibikie ntarasi.” 
3  Neitoki olaiguanani aibelekenya nemayian ina umata oo Siraeli, eitashe ina umata pooki oo Siraeli. 
4   Nejo ninye, “Meisisi Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel, amu eitabayie ninye te nkaina enye ina apa naisiligie te nkutuk enye Daudi papaai lai, ejo, 
5  ‘Ore ebaiki ina olong nayaua nanu iltung'ana laainei aitupuku te nkop e Misiri, eitu nanu agelu enkanasa tiatua Israel pooki, naa ninye eshetieki enkaji, pee etum enkarna ai ataa ine etii. Neitu nanu agelu oltung'ani aitaa kitok te shumata iltung'ana laainei loo Siraeli. 
6  Kake ategelua nanu Yerusalem pee etum enkarna ai ataa ine etii, nategelua nanu Daudi pee eitasheiki iltung'ana laainei le Israel.’ 
7  Eeta apa Daudi papaai lai to ltau lenye pee eshet enkaji tenkaraki enkarna o Laitoriani, Enkai e Israel. 
8  Kake etiaaka Olaitoriani Daudi papaai lai, ‘Ore hoo niata to ltau lino pee ishet enkaji tenkaraki enkarna ai, intobira amu iata ina to ltau lino; 
9  ore ake eyia, milo iyie ashet ina aji, kake olayioni lino likiikini iyie, ninye olo ashet enkaji tenkaraki enkarna ai.’ 
10  Eitabayie taata Olaitoriani ina kisiligata enye apa naisiligishore; amu aitasho nanu te rishata e Daudi, papaai lai, naton to lorika le nkitoo, le Israel, anaa apa enaisiligishore Olaitoriani natesheta nanu enkaji tenkaraki enkarna o Laitoriani, Enkai e Israel. 
11  Natipika ine osanduku laa ninye etii ilo sotua lo Laitoriani oitobira ninye tenebo iltung'ana loo Siraeli.”

Enkomono e Solomon


12  Neitashe Solomon te dukuya ilo perere lo lasar lo Laitoriani te dukuya ina umata pooki neilepie nkaik enyena aitorioo. 
13  Eitobira apa Solomon ewueji o suyai neika ntemat are e nkaina enkadoro o endapasho, naa entemata nabo enkadoro nailep, nepik apa ine wueji olgoriet. neitashe te nchumata. Neitoki agil kung te nchumata ine te dukuya ina umata pooki oo Siraeli neitorioo nkaik enyena aing'orie shumata, 
14  nejo, “Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel, meetae Enkai natiu anaa iyie, te keper o te nkop, naibung osotua neitodolu enyorrata nauno too sinkan lenyena oopuo te dukuya iyie too ltauja lenye pooki. 
15  Mbung'a iyie tialo osinka lino Daudi, papaai lai ina apa nimbalakinye ninye; ee iroro iyie te nkutuk ino, nintabayie te nkaina ino nena ena olong. 
16   Ore naa taata, Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel, mbung'a to sinka lino Daudi, papaai lai, ina apa nisiligie ninye, ijo, “Mikiany ae kata oltung'ani kisiaai iyie te dukuya nanu, pee etonie olorika le nkitoo le Israel, oi duoo tenaa kejurru ilayiok linono nkoitoi enye nepuo too nkitanapat aainei anaa enishomie iyie te dukuya nanu.” 
17  Ore naa taata Olaitoriani, Enkai e Israel, nchoo eunoyu ilo rorei lino, apa lirorie osinka lino Daudi.


18   “Kake amaa, kesipa kebik Olaitoriani tenebo iltung'ana te nkop? Ng'ura, ore keper o keper nalakua nemikiishaa iyie; kebaa naa mikiishaa iyie ena aji natesheta nanu! 
19  Toning'o naa enkomono o sinka lino o esayiata enye, Olaitoriani Enkai ai. Toning'o enkishirata o enkomono nayau osinka lino dukuya iyie; 
20   pee etum nkonyek inono aaing'ura ena aji dama o kewarie, ene wueji apa nisiligishore pee ipik enkarna ino, pee itum atoning'o enkomono naomon osinka lino tene wueji. 
21  Toning'o iyie eomonokinoto o sinka lino o enoo ltung'ana linono le Israel, te neomon eing'or ene wueji, ee toning'o iyie itii emanyisho ino te keper, naa te nining nipalaki.


22  “Teneas oltung'ani eng'oki tialo ole latia enye, neinosieki olmumai lenye te dukuya ele perere lo lasar tena aji, 
23  toning'o naa iyie itii keper, nias, ninguanare isinkan linono, aitalaku entorroni ayau entorroni enye shumata endukuya enye makewan, nimbalunye ilo supat alaaki ninye te risioroto e supatisho enye.


24  “Tenemiri iltung'ana linono loo Siraeli te dukuya ilmang'ati, enkaraki nataasa ninche eng'oki te iyie, tenelo neibelekenya ninche aaibalie enkarna ino, neomon, nesaisho tiatua ena aji, 
25  toning'o ake iyie itii keper, nipalaki eng'oki oo ltung'ana linono loo Siraeli, nirrinyu ninche menyaaki aapuonu ina kop apa ninchoo ninche o loo menye.


26  “Teneikeno keper, nelai enchan tenkaraki nataasa ninche eng'oki tialo iyie, teneomon ninche eing'or ene wueji, neibalie enkarna ino, neibelekenya aaing'uaa ing'ok enye, itoosho iyie ninche, 
27  toning'o naa iyie itii keper, nipalaki eng'oki oo sinkan linono, iltung'ana linono loo Siraeli, niutaki ninche enkoitoi sidai naa ninye epuoyie; nirriwaki enchan ena kop ino, naa ninye inchoo iltung'ana linono metaa enjung'ore.


28  “Tenelotu olameyu enkop anaa olmeitai, anaa erruoyo ndaiki naatii nkurman, anaa tenelotu olmaati, anaa enkurto; teneng'adu ilmang'ati lenye ninche te nabo ake ninye oo nkanas enye; o pooki meitai anaa pooki muoyian; 
29  ore ake enkomono pooki o esayiata naomon oltung'ani obo anaa iltung'ana pooki loo Siraeli, eyiolo ake oltung'ani eoshoto enye o sina lenye, neitorioo nkaik aaing'orie ena aji; 
30  toning'o naa iyie te keper, teina manyisho ino, nipalaki, ore ake pooki tau liyiolo iyie nilaaki te risioroto oo nkoitoi enyena (Amu iyie ake openy oyiolo iltauja loo nkera e tung'ana); 
31  pee kitum ninche aatureita iyie, nepuo too nkoitoi inono, nkolong'i pooki naaishu teina kop apa ninchoo iloo menye.


32  “Naa tenelotu oltung'ani loo loreren, ilo leme oloo ltung'ana linono loo Siraeli eing'uaa enelakua tenkaraki enkarna ino kitok, o enkarna ino magilani, tenelotu ninye aomon eing'or ena aji, 
33  toning'o iyie itii keper, ina manyisho ino, nias te risioroto e nena pooki nikimpotie ilo tung'ani loo loreren iyie; pee etum iloreren pooki le nkop aatayiolo enkarna ino, nikiureyu iyie, anaa enaasita iltung'ana linono loo Siraeli, netum aatayiolo nchere ore ena aji natesheta nanu te nkarna ino naa enkarna ino eipotieki.


34  “Tenepuo iltung'ana linono olarrabal aagilunore ilmang'ati lenye, ore te pooki oitoi niimie iyie ninche; nikiomon ninche iyie eing'or ena anasa nitegelua, iyie o ena aji natesheta nanu te nkarna ino, 
35  toning'o iyie itii keper enkomono enye o esayiata enye, nintagol ninche.


36  “Teneas ninche eng'oki te dukuya iyie, amu meetae oltung'ani lemias ing'ok, nigorokino iyie ninche, ninchooyo ninche too lmang'ati lenye nenapi ninche aaya eyararoto te nkop nalakua o enataana; 
37  kake tenedamu ninche too ltauja teina kop apa nawaki ninche, neirridu, nikisai ninche iyie teina kop e yararoto enye, ejo, ‘Kitaasa iyiook eng'oki, nikitaasa ntorrok’; 
38  teneirridu ninche too ndamunot enye pooki o too ltauja lenye pooki teina kop e yararoto enye, apa naawaki ninche, neomon eing'or ina kop enye apa ninchoo iyie loo menye, oina anasa nitegelua iyie, o ina aji natesheta nanu tenkaraki enkarna ino, 
39  toning'o iyie itii keper ina manyisho ino, enkomono enye o esayiata enye. Ntagolo ninche, nipalaki lelo tung'ana linono ootaasa eng'oki te iyie. 
40  Ore naa taata Enkai ai nchoo eing'or nkonyek inono nening nkiyiaa inono enkomono ene wueji.


41   “Naa tudumunye taata, Olaitoriani Enkai, shomo

ewueji ino enkiyeng'iyeng, iyie oilo sanduku lino le magilanisho.

Nchoo ilapolosak linono Olaitoriani Enkai meishopokini enjeunoto ino.

Nchoo isinyat linono eshipakino esupatisho ino.


42  Olaitoriani Enkai, mimbelekeny enkomom ino aitung'uaa

ilo lino otubukokoki eilata aaput!

Tadamu enyorrata ino nauno tenkaraki Daudi osinka lino.”

